<section class="about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <h2 class="section-title" id="about-heading">About</h2>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>
      I'm <strong>Liang Dongjing</strong>, an indie iOS developer and photographer based in China.
      I build focused, well-crafted apps that do one thing well — from
      <a href="https://getcontura.com">Contura</a>, a 3D body tracker, to
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/buzzcam-proraw-burst-camera/id6758300007">BuzzCam</a>, a ProRAW burst camera.
      I believe great tools should stay out of your way.
    </p>
    <p>
      Behind the lens, I'm drawn to quiet moments: golden-hour light, urban architecture,
      and landscapes at dawn. I shoot with an iPhone and a Canon EOS 700D.
      Photography, for me, is about learning to see.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

